These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-1::.
Sport: ice-hockey, climbing, weightlifting
1. Sport:climbing is on the right of Sport:weightlifting##1
2. Sport:ice-hockey is on the far right##1
3. Sport:ice-hockey is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |       2       |   3   |
| Sport   | weightlifting | climbing | ice-hockey |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-2::.
Food: pineapple, eggplant, grapes
1. Food:eggplant is in an odd position##4
2. Food:pineapple is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1    |     2      |   3    |
| Food   | pineapple | grapes | eggplant |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-3::.
Hobby: card-games, filmmaking, photography
1. Hobby:filmmaking is in an even position##4
2. Hobby:filmmaking is on the left or right of Hobby:photography##3
3. Hobby:photography is on the right of Hobby:filmmaking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |      3       |
| Hobby   | card-games | filmmaking | photography |

 #################################
 
